      "text": [
        " اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ أَصْبَحَ مُعَافًى فِي بَدَنِهِ مُخَلًّى فِي سَرْبِهِ عِنْدَهُ قُوتُ يَوْمِهِ فَكَأَنَّمَا حِيزَتْ لَهُ اَلدُّنْيَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5916 - Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) said:\n\"Whoever begins his day in good health, secure in his surroundings, and has the sustenance for his day, it is as if the entire world has been gathered for him.\""
        ]
      }
    },
